  {
   "start": 1.36,
   "end": 8.68,
   "text": "Hello, living in Boulder V-Log for the 21st of January."
  },
  {
   "start": 11.18,
   "end": 12.9,
   "text": "I'm super high right now."
  },
  {
   "start": 12.96,
   "end": 18.54,
   "text": "I just got really high to smoke much weed at 7.15 in the morning."
  },
  {
   "start": 20.22,
   "end": 29.5,
   "text": "So yesterday, I think I finally crashed at like 3 or something."
  },
  {
   "start": 29.5,
   "end": 35.02,
   "text": "But then I woke up again at like 1.30 or something."
  },
  {
   "start": 36.6,
   "end": 39.14,
   "text": "I don't remember what time I crashed, but I got up at like 1.30."
  },
  {
   "start": 39.32,
   "end": 42.48,
   "text": "I've been up since then, so I feel kind of tired, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 42.72,
   "end": 48.24,
   "text": "But I'm pretty close to finishing Pliny."
  },
  {
   "start": 48.42,
   "end": 53.38,
   "text": "I wanted to do this one other thing, though,"
  },
  {
   "start": 53.38,
