   "text": "Is where in the tops of every chapter you can jump to the menu that it's in."
  },
  {
   "start": 61.92,
   "end": 63.68,
   "text": "Because you don't have the menu on top."
  },
  {
   "start": 64.66,
   "end": 66.7,
   "text": "So you'd want to be able to jump to it."
  },
  {
   "start": 66.94,
   "end": 69.12,
   "text": "And so, yeah, I'm pasting those on."
  },
  {
   "start": 69.22,
   "end": 70.68,
   "text": "So that's just the final step."
  },
  {
   "start": 70.84,
   "end": 73.62,
   "text": "And then I'll paste it."
  },
  {
   "start": 73.66,
   "end": 75.6,
   "text": "Yeah, so then I think tomorrow I'll be like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 75.6,
   "end": 76.82,
   "text": "Yeah, Pliny."
  },
  {
